# Build context is the monorepo root for any Dockerfile under apps/.
# Docker reads .dockerignore alongside the build context, so keep this
# at the repo root (not next to a per-app Dockerfile).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/.vite-plus
**/.turbo
**/.tsbuildinfo
**/*.log
.git
.github
**/.DS_Store
